Rule: If `marital_status` is `Married`, then the likelihood of earning more than 50k increases.
If `education` is `Doctorate`, then the likelihood of earning more than 50k increases.
If `workclass` is `Self-Employed`, then the likelihood of earning more than 50k increases.
If `age` is significantly higher (e.g., 90), then the likelihood of earning more than 50k increases.
